  "title": "Accounts and Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>Long Zhou Engineering is established as Gas Pipe and Earthwork specialist in Singapore. We have worked with a numerous satisfied of clients including, small and medium sized enterprises, government bodies and residential consumers. </p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support the finance manager by maintaining accurate bookkeeping records, preparing purchase orders, and assisting with project claim submissions to ensure smooth financial operations.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain accurate bookkeeping records to support the finance manager’s financial tracking and reporting</li><li>Prepare purchase orders following company procedures to facilitate timely procurement</li><li>Assist in compiling and submitting project claims to ensure proper documentation and timely reimbursement</li><li>Use Excel, Google Sheets, and office software to organize projects data and generate claim reports efficiently</li><li>Complete assigned tasks within deadlines while maintaining a positive and proactive work attitude</li></ul>",
